name: DeepLIFT
text: Implements DeepLIFT algorithm for the neuron.

name: Feature Ablation
text: A perturbation based approach to computing neuron attribution, involving replacing each input feature with a given baseline.

name: Gradient
text: Computes the gradient of the output of a particular neuron with respect to the inputs of the network.

name: Gradient SHAP
text: Implements gradient SHAP for a neuron in a hidden layer.

name: Guided Backprop
text: Computes attribution of the given neuron using guided backpropagation.

name: Integrated Gradients
text: Approximates the integral of gradients for a particular neuron.

name: Conductance
text: Computes conductance with respect to particular hidden neuron.
